title: Summer at the Inn
description:
Our story tonight is called Summer at the Inn and it’s a story about a morning by the lake at the great old house. It’s also about setting a table with care, a blue jay sitting at a feeder and how to borrow someone’s else’s joy and wear it as your own.  So get cozy and ready to sleep.
